  <section>
    <h2>Browser Support</h2>
    <p>The <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> element is supported in all modern browsers. The <code>name</code> attribute for exclusive accordions is supported in Chrome 120+, Safari 17.2+, and Firefox 130+. The <code>::details-content</code> animation pseudo-element works in Chrome 131+ and Safari 17.5+; other browsers fall back to instant show/hide.</p>
  </section>
